Entry Point
===========

 - http://127.0.0.1:60080/demo/thruk/ (traefik loadbalancer)
 - Login is omdadmin / omd

Setup
=====

 - 3 clustered thruk nodes based on the thruk/ folder
 - 1 traefik load balancer
 - 1 omd site used as backend for the thruk nodes
     also used as mysql database
 - use "./scale <nr>" to change number of thruk containers
